original_title: Adventures in Europe - Vol 5 Amsterdam Pride
overview: It's time for Amsterdam Pride! The biggest gay celebration in the world. Big D is back in his favorite city for an all new adventure. Amsterdam is the gay capital of the world and it's Canal Parade is the highlight of this weekend long event. Millions of visitors from all over the world flock to this city to witness this amazing spectacle of gay pride. Big D gets an exclusive tour and more.
title: Adventures in Europe - Vol 5 Amsterdam Pride
